      <description>
        <![CDATA[<h1>[AI编程从入门到入土] 规范</h1><p>作者：byzh（xxx@example.com）</p>
        
          <h1 id="项目规范">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e9%a1%b9%e7%9b%ae%e8%a7%84%e8%8c%83"></a>
项目规范
</h1><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">my_project/
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">├── data/                     # 存放数据集（原始/处理后）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   └── README.md             # 说明数据来源、格式、预处理方式
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">├── models/                   # 模型定义
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   ├── __init__.py          
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   ├── loss.py               
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   └── cnn.py                
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">├── training/                 # 训练脚本
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   ├── __init__.py
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   └── train_cnn.py          # 原 s03_01_train_cnn.py
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">├── clustering/               # 聚类算法
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   ├── __init__.py
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   ├── minibatchkmeans.py    
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   ├── bisectingkmeans.py    
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   ├── faisskmeans.py       
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   ├── birch.py              
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   └── hdbscan.py            
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">├── visualization/            # 可视化脚本
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   ├── __init__.py
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   ├── t_sne.py            
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   ├── umap.py              
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   └── pacmap.py            
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">├── utils/                    # 工具函数（可选，如数据加载、日志、配置）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   ├── __init__.py
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   └── helpers.py
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">├── configs/                  # 配置文件（如超参数、路径）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   └── config.yaml
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">├── scripts/                  # 主运行脚本（可选，封装命令行入口）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   └── run_pipeline.py       # 可调用各模块的主流程
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">├── logs/                     # 训练/运行日志
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">├── outputs/                  # 输出结果（模型、聚类结果、可视化图）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">├── requirements.txt          # 依赖包列表
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">├── README.md                 # 项目说明、安装、使用指南
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">└── .gitignore                # Git忽略文件
</span></span></code></pre></div>
        
        <hr><p>本文2026-05-17首发于<a href='http://localhost:1313/'>byzh的博客</a>，最后修改于2026-05-17</p>]]>
